## Creating VPC-peering using CLI (Automation)

List of commands to be used: 
Creating a peering: 
* aws ec2 create-vpc-peering-connection --vpc-id <YOUR_VPC_ID> --peer-vpc-id <PEER_VPC_ID> --region us-east-1
Accepting a peering:
*aws ec2 accept-vpc-peering-connection --vpc-peering-connection-id <PEERING_CONNECTION_ID> --region <REGION>
*Adding Route-Table

